#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn38.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn38.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Arahattapañhāsutta "
msgstr "2. A Question About Perfection "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.1"
msgid "“‘Arahattaṃ, arahattan’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘perfection’. "

msgctxt "sn38.2:1.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, arahattan”ti? "
msgstr "What is perfection?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.3"
msgid "“Yo kho, āvuso, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "“Reverend, the ending of greed, hate, and delusion "

msgctxt "sn38.2:1.4"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati arahattan”ti. "
msgstr "is called perfection.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.5"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for realizing this perfection?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.6"
msgid "“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.7"
msgid "“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“Well, what is it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.8"
msgid "“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāya, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn38.2:1.9"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn38.2:1.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo, ayaṃ paṭipadā etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the path, the practice, for realizing this perfection.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.11"
msgid "“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā etassa arahattassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "“Reverend, this is a fine path, a fine practice, for realizing this perfection. "

msgctxt "sn38.2:1.12"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Just this much is enough to be diligent.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.2:1.13"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

